            "title": "Rediscovery of Histiotus alienus Thomas, 1916 a century after its description (Chiroptera, Vespertilionidae): distribution extension and redescription",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Vinícius C.",
                    "lastName": "Cláudio"
                },
                {
